text: Tims Thicket Beach Tims Thicket, sometimes spelled Tim's Thicket, is an area of Crown land within Dawesville, Western Australia that is known for its waste treatment facility, and for access to Tims Thicket Beach, a four-wheel drive area. The 4WD beach area starts at Tims Thicket in the north and runs south to Preston Beach. ==References== Category:Beaches of Western Australia Category:Mandurah Category:Off-roading
